The paper also mentions optimal constructions for tree metrics, which falls under the category of discrete mathematics (cs.DM). The construction involves tradeoffs and optimization, which suggests the use of numerical analysis techniques (cs.NA). Finally, the paper mentions the use of random point sets, which could involve statistical inference and machine learning techniques (cs.SI).
